#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.fft"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:1 of
msgid "Compute the one-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform."
msgstr "计算一维离散傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the one-dimensional *n*-point discrete Fourier "
"Transform (DFT) with the efficient Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) algorithm"
" [CT]."
msgstr ""
"此函数使用高效的快速傅里叶变换（FFT）算法 [CT] 计算一维 *n* 点离散傅里叶"
"变换（DFT）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:7 of
msgid "Input tensor, can be complex."
msgstr "输入张量，可以是复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:9 of
msgid ""
"Length of the transformed axis of the output. If `n` is smaller than the "
"length of the input, the input is cropped. If it is larger, the input is "
"padded with zeros.  If `n` is not given, the length of the input along "
"the axis specified by `axis` is used."
msgstr ""
"输出变换轴的长度。如果 `n` 小于输入的长度，则输入将被裁剪；如果 `n` 较大"
"，则输入将用零填充。如果未给出 `n`，则使用沿 `axis` 指定轴的输入长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:14 of
msgid "Axis over which to compute the FFT.  If not given, the last axis is used."
msgstr "用于计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:17 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axis"
" indicated by `axis`, or the last one if `axis` is not specified."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿着由 `axis` 指定的轴进行变换，如果没有"
"指定 `axis`，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:24 of
msgid "if `axes` is larger than the last axis of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axes` 大于 `a` 的最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:29 of
msgid "for definition of the DFT and conventions used."
msgstr "有关 DFT 定义和所用约定的信息。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ifft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:32 of
msgid "The inverse of `fft`."
msgstr "`fft` 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:35 of
msgid "The two-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "二维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:38 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "*n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:41 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT of real input."
msgstr "实数输入的 *n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftfreq`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:44 of
msgid "Frequency bins for given FFT parameters."
msgstr "给定 FFT 参数的频率区间。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:47 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:48 of
msgid ""
"FFT (Fast Fourier Transform) refers to a way the discrete Fourier "
"Transform (DFT) can be calculated efficiently, by using symmetries in the"
" calculated terms.  The symmetry is highest when `n` is a power of 2, and"
" the transform is therefore most efficient for these sizes."
msgstr ""
"FFT（快速傅里叶变换）是一种通过利用计算项中的对称性高效计算离散傅里叶变换"
"（DFT）的方法。当 `n` 是 2 的幂时对称性最高，因此变换对于这些大小最为高效"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:53 of
msgid ""
"The DFT is defined, with the conventions used in this implementation, in "
"the documentation for the `numpy.fft` module."
msgstr "此实现中使用的 DFT 定义及约定，请参阅 `numpy.fft` 模块的文档。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:57 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:58 of
msgid ""
"Cooley, James W., and John W. Tukey, 1965, \"An algorithm for the machine"
" calculation of complex Fourier series,\" *Math. Comput.* 19: 297-301."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:63 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.fft.fft:72 of
msgid ""
"In this example, real input has an FFT which is Hermitian, i.e., "
"symmetric in the real part and anti-symmetric in the imaginary part, as "
"described in the `numpy.fft` documentation:"
msgstr ""
"在此示例中，实数输入的FFT是Hermitian的，即如`numpy.fft`文档中所述，实部"
"对称而虚部反对称："

